      • registerToken

        void registerToken(org.spongepowered.api.plugin.PluginContainer pluginContainer,
                   java.lang.String tokenName,
                   PlaceholderParser parser)
        Registers a token.
        Parameters:
        pluginContainer - The PluginContainer that wants to register the token
        tokenName - The name of the token to register. This will be converted to lowercase.
        parser - The parser to register.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the token name contains whitespace, :, | or _
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if the token name has already been registered
